rows.label: tlk45400251_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Superbia has been trading with Invidia
more often lately. Something to do with
the economy booming, I suppose?

rows.label: tlk45400251_04_msg0002
rows.name:
So I came up with the idea for a
new bread confection using an Invidian
fruit called Ruby Mangosteen.

rows.label: tlk45400251_04_msg0003
rows.name:
A fruity bun that's warm
on the outside, but cool
and sweet on the inside!

rows.label: tlk45400251_04_msg0004
rows.name:
It's called the Hot Ruby Steamed Bun!
You might have heard of it already.
Bet you didn't know I invented it!

rows.label: tlk45400251_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Shenka's selling them at her store
right now, so you should definitely
try some if you haven't.

rows.label: tlk45400251_04_msg0006
rows.name:
It's funny, though. A little while back,
I would never have dreamed we'd be able
to use ingredients from Invidia.

rows.label: tlk45400251_04_msg0007
rows.name:
I guess we should be thankful
to a certain someone for that.
